WHAT MAKES A HIDDEN GEM:
- Small-to-medium market cap ($50M-$10B)
- Strong fundamentals (revenue growth, improving margins, healthy balance sheet)
- Undervalued relative to peers or growth potential
- Positive technical setup (accumulation, breakout patterns)
- Emerging catalysts not yet priced in
- Low institutional ownership or analyst coverage
- Positioned in growing industries/trends
- Manageable risks (not value traps)

HOW TO USE:
1. Enter any small-cap stock ticker (e.g., CRWD, PLTR, SNOW)
2. AI agents search the web for:
   - Technical breakout signals
   - Fundamental undervaluation
   - Emerging positive catalysts
   - Industry growth trends
   - Risk assessment
3. View comprehensive analysis with conviction score
4. Detailed tabs show what the market is missing

The app is ready to discover hidden gems before they go mainstream!
